		<h3>Transfusion-Alternative Health Care&#8212;Meeting Patient Needs and Rights</h3>
		<p>Health-care professionals are keenly interested in meeting each patient&#8217;s medical needs. Thus, they welcome new therapies and approaches that can help them do this. They realize, too, that governments and society are increasingly giving attention to the patient&#8217;s ethical views and legal rights.</p>
<p>Available in:  English<br>
Length: 28 minutes</p>
<p>Medical professionals are invited to call Hospital Information Services at 718-560-4300.</p>

